data.description: Discover the perfect sanctuary for your family in the serene picturesque Lehigh Acres FL. This stunning house situated on a spacious 1/2 acres lot, offers a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. With 3 bedrooms plus a den and 2 full bathrooms, it provides ample space for everyone to enjoy. The newly updated appliances and kitchen granite countertops add a touch of sophistication to the heart of the house. The guest bathroom is designed in a convenient Jack and Jill style, ensuring privacy and convenience for both guests and family members. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home. Call now for a private showing!
